lyrics:
[Verse 1]
On a distant shore, in lands far apart
Isaiah and Elizabeth, captured by destiny's chart
Both lost in a world, so vast and wide
Their hearts unaware, they were bound to collide

[Chorus]
Bubu and Dudu, their love so true
Across oceans and mountains, their hearts pursued
Through trials they'll weather, without a doubt
Isaiah and Elizabeth, forever they'll shout
